sequenceDiagram
    participant Code as Your Code
    participant Render as render()
    participant Tree as Element Tree
    participant Diff as Diff Engine
    participant GPU as GPU

    Code->>Code: State changes
    Code->>Render: cx.notify()
    Render->>Tree: Build new tree<br/>(hundreds of elements)
    Note over Tree: Lightweight construction<br/>minimal allocation

    Tree->>Diff: Compare with previous tree
    Diff->>Diff: Calculate minimal changes
    Note over Diff: Only changed elements<br/>identified

    Diff->>GPU: Update changed elements only
    GPU->>GPU: Hardware-accelerated render

    Note over Code,GPU: Cost: tree construction (cheap)<br/>Benefit: no manual optimization needed
